# File size limits

Read and follow `PROJECT_FILE_SIZE_RULES.md` in the repo root.

- Target **~300 lines** per hand-written `.dart` file; never exceed **400**.
- Extract UI to `presentation/widgets/` with descriptive names (`dashboard_countdown_card.dart`).
- Extract router groups to `presentation/router/app_router_*_routes.dart`.
- Exempt generated l10n and `*.g.dart`.

When editing a file near the limit, split **before** adding more code.
